message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with visual question answering (VQA) task, specifically chart question answering (CQA), which requires fine-grained measurements, optical character recognition, and handling out-of-vocabulary words in both questions and answers. These are all areas of research that fall under computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
